Given the following program and the variable in complex data type, decompose the it into variables with primary data type.. The program is struct c_new {
  int h : 18;
  int g;
} i, j;
int main() {
  struct c_new l;
  l.h = j.h;
  int n = j.h && l.h;
  int p = l.h | -(165 && l.h) - n;
  i.g = p;
}
.                 The target to be optimized is `int g`.
